Get billing information for the current user.

**Parameters:** None.

```graphql
query GetBilling {
  billing {
    billing {
      credits
      creditsUsed
      creditsLimit
      subscriptionPlan
      subscriptionPeriod
      subscriptionStatus
      subscriptionStartedAt
      subscriptionEndsAt
      usagePercentage
    }
  }
}
